{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was trained during the First World War as a volunteer nurse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so when we had-- we saw that eventually we'd have to emigrate, she took a refresher course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in fact, when we came to this country, she was-- she-- she took an exam, in a language she barely knew, and started working as a private-duty nurse.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She later stopped that and, you know, did other things, but--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we lived at a number of addresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the one I can remember best was Feldberg Platz [GERMAN], that-- it is 15.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "F-E-L-D-B-E-R-G P-L-A-T-Z.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Feldberg was a mountain in the Taunus range, which was quite a bit away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only 800 meters high.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on a clear day, we could look out of our window on the Feldberg Platz and see the Feldberg across the Rhine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's become rather hazy now and I don't think one can see this very often anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we could look from our balcony and see the-- and that's why it was called Feldberg Platz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the place where you could see the Feldberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the one I know, I remember best, because we lived there from 1930 to 1937.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before, we had lived in the Kaiser Strasse, which was the big boulevard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And afterwards, we lived on the Kaiser Strasse again, but it-- we had to move out of this beautiful house of which I will show you a-- a picture.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- because it was owned by non-Jews and we had to move into a house that was owned by Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we moved into-- it was not-- not very far away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was not a bad apartment, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this particular apartment was spectacular, in a spectacular house.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
